用户在旧操作系统上使用先进格式化设备时，使用硬盘制造商提供的软件重新对齐磁盘很重要。对于避免所谓''跨分配单元''的性能降级问题，即偏移的分区导致文件系统分配单元跨越多个物理磁盘分区，磁盘重新对齐是很有必要的。由于分配单元到扇区的对齐时在创建硬盘分区时决定的，而重对齐软件是在创建硬盘分区''之后''使用的。这有助于减少计算生态系统生成的未对齐写的数量。为了让应用程序准备向高级格式技术过渡而开展的进一步活动是由"高级格式技术委员会"（即先前的''长数据扇区委员会''）<ref name="idema">{{cite web |url=http://idema.org/?page_id=2012 |title=About the Advanced Format Technology Committee (formerly LDS Committee) |website=[[IDEMA|www.idema.org]] |access-date=14 December 2020 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160330222036/http://idema.org/?page_id=2012 |archive-date=30 March 2016 |url-status=live}}</ref><ref name="snia">{{cite web |url=https://www.snia.org/sites/default/orig/sdc_archives/2008_presentations/tuesday/MikeFitzpatrick_IDEMA_4kB_Sector.pdf |title=4kB Data Sector Update - IDEMA 4kB Technical Committee |website=[[Storage_Networking_Industry_Association|www.snia.org]] |date=September 2008 |access-date=14 December 2020 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160811075536/http://www.snia.org/sites/default/orig/sdc_archives/2008_presentations/tuesday/MikeFitzpatrick_IDEMA_4kB_Sector.pdf |archive-date=11 August 2016 |url-status=live}}</ref>和硬盘制造商带头进行的。<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.seagate.com/docs/pdf/en-GB/whitepaper/tp615_smartalign_for_af_4k.pdf |title=SmartAlign™ Technology for Advanced Format Hard Drives |website=[[Seagate_Technology|www.seagate.com]] |year=2010 |access-date=14 December 2020 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101129221035/https://www.seagate.com/docs/pdf/en-GB/whitepaper/tp615_smartalign_for_af_4k.pdf |archive-date=29 November 2010 |url-status=live}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.hitachigst.com/internal-drives/advanced-format-drives |title=Download the Hitachi Align Tool |website=[[HGST|www.hitachigst.com]] |year=2010 |access-date=14 December 2020 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110623202837/http://www.hitachigst.com/internal-drives/advanced-format-drives |archivedate=23 June 2011}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://support.wdc.com/product